  "questions": [
    {
      "text": "<p>Prema razgovoru, koja rečenica pokazuje ispravnu upotrebu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">going to</span> prema trenutnim dokazima?</p>",
      "answers": [
        {
          "answer": "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">We will probably use React since it's a popular choice these days.</span></p>",
          "feedback": "<p>Ova rečenica koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">will</span> za akciju koja bi mogla da se dogodi kasnije, a koja ne odražava odluku donetu na osnovu trenutnih dokaza.</p>",
          "audioId": null
        },
        {
          "answer": "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">I think we will go with Node.js for the back-end, considering our team's expertise.</span></p>",
          "feedback": "<p>Ovde, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">will</span> se koristi za buduću akciju prema trenutnom stanju, ali <span class=\"highlighted-text\">going to</span> bi bio precizniji jer odluka izgleda zavisiti od trenutne stručnosti tima.</p>",
          "audioId": null
        },
        {
          "answer": "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">We're going to need a UX designer because the project is complex.</span></p>",
          "feedback": null,
          "audioId": null
        },
        {
          "answer": "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">I will call the designer since we're going to need one for this project.</span></p>",
          "feedback": "<p>Ova rečenica koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">will</span> za naglu odluku (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">calling the designer</span>), koja je tačna, ali ne pokazuje upotrebu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">going to</span> prema trenutnim dokazima.</p>",
          "audioId": null
        }
      ],
      "solution": 3
    }
  ],
